                        </persName>, grants and quitclaims to
                        <persName>
                           <forename>Roger</forename> de
                     <surname>Bradebrug</surname>
                        </persName> his brother all right and claim in 4
                  messuages, 25 acres of land, and 2 acres of meadow in the meadow called
