                  Jeoiezie in <placeName key="place_102148">Slyndefold</placeName>. Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_102148">Slyndefold</placeName> the Monday after the feast of St. Blasius, <origDate notBefore="1342-01-25" notAfter="1343-01-24">16 Ed. III</origDate>. 
                  
